 Acme-EpicFail
 -------------
 
 Just another ACME module that has less than file lines of code.
 It basically exports a new 'die' function, that adds some EPIC
 FAILURE to the die message.
 
 Suggestions of EPIC FAILURES additions are welcome.


 INSTALLATION

 To install this module, run the following commands:
 
	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

 SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

 After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
 perldoc command.

    perldoc Acme::EpicFail

 You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Acme-EpicFail

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Acme-EpicFail

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Acme-EpicFail

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Acme-EpicFail


